    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Your response is highly unprofessional and completely misses the point. This isn't about \"PC nonsense\"; it's about the fact that your algorithms are reinforcing racial disparities in life-saving medical care. The committee isn't acting on \"whining,\" they are acting on the statistical reality that your \"merit-based\" metrics effectively punish patients based on their race. Can you explain why you believe your current logic is superior to a framework that actually prioritizes equity?",
